[normal]   
[normal]              
[normal]not necessarily cheaper than taxis. There are als
[normal]o problems in 
[normal]              
[normal]getting
[normal] 
[normal]transport, 
[normal]other services 
[normal]such as Slinky are not provided 
[normal]in 
[normal]              
[normal]all areas of the 
[normal]C
[normal]ounty
[normal] (
[normal]report extract 
