[normal]If you have a 
[normal]              
[normal]concessionary pass, depending on 
[normal]which service 
[normal]you use, you 
[normal]              
[normal]can use your bus p
[normal]ass.  
[normal]Slinky is limited to certain areas and it 
[normal]              
[normal]doesn’t cross boundaries
[normal], they serve the local communities in the 
[normal]              
[normal]areas they are based.
[normal] “
[normal]If one person wants it in the north and then 
[normal]              
