[normal]              
[normal]No community transport is available in the evenings to provide 
[normal]              
[normal]transport for disabled people to attend groups. This can be a vital 
[normal]              
[normal]way of preventing isolation.
[normal] 
[normal]Taxis[bold]              
[normal]When disabled people have to use taxis to get to appointments 
[normal]              
[normal]because of lack of availability of public transport they need to have 
[normal]              
[normal]a known company to use as access can vary e.g. the ramps used 
[normal]              
[normal]for powered chairs are not always to the same safety standards.
